  <h1>Is Klaviyo free?</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    <strong>Klaviyo is free up to 500 email contacts</strong> — beyond that, paid plans start at approximately $45/month and scale sharply, reaching $400/month at 10,000 contacts. For most growing Shopify stores, Klaviyo becomes one of the largest monthly app costs within 12–18 months of launch.
  </p>

  <div class="meta-row">
