    <span>READ TIME: 3 min</span>
    <span>CATEGORY: Email Marketing</span>
  </div>

  <h2>// Klaviyo Free Plan — Exact Limits</h2>
  <p>
    The Klaviyo free plan is available only to accounts with 500 email contacts or fewer. At 500 contacts, you can send up to 500 emails per month — that is a 1:1 send-to-contact ratio, meaning you cannot send a single campaign to your full list more than once per month. Email support is available only for the first 60 days on the free plan. All emails sent on the free plan include "Sent by Klaviyo" branding in the footer, which you cannot remove without upgrading.
  </p>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <div class="label">⚠ IMPORTANT — FREE PLAN LIMITS</div>
    <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px;">Klaviyo counts your <strong>total profile count</strong> toward the 500-contact limit — not just active subscribers. If you import 400 customers from Shopify who haven't opted in to marketing, those still count toward your limit. Many merchants hit the 500 threshold faster than expected.</p>
  </div>

