      <button class="faq-question">Is Systeme.io a real Klaviyo replacement for Shopify?<span class="chevron">▾</span></button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes — for most Shopify stores. Systeme.io supports email automation flows, segmentation, and Shopify integration via webhooks. It handles the four flows that drive 80% of e-commerce email revenue: welcome series, abandoned cart, post-purchase, and win-back. The primary limitation is that it lacks Shopify's native app integration — you connect via webhooks or Make.com rather than a one-click install. The full migration guide is at <a href="/replace-klaviyo-free">stackarchitect.xyz/replace-klaviyo-free</a>.
